Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my secret technique, the Sweets Canyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-she let one box of candy slide\Nso it would take down that whole mountain of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,UMR stuck it to us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Her techniques are as Godlike as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,UMR, that was a fine play, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we go somewhere and eat these?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Do you know someplace good?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,H... H...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How about coming to my house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? To your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all I've seen is her living room and the study.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'd be glad to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... so this is your room, TSF? It's really big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep eyeing it like that,\Nyou'll make me embarrassed, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So many trophies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! And look at those goods from Anumate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She even put up the photos\Nfrom when we went to the amusement park...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in a friend's room is fun\Nbecause it brings back memories, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sbrite is the perfect accompaniment for snacks, UMR!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to watch anime while enjoying snacks\Nand drinking Sbrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Sylphin has been having "feasts" of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm pretty particular\Nabout that sort of thing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you show me how it's done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I suppose everyone does this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know? Switching between chocolate\Nand potato chips makes them extra delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Indeed, I have never tried that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Bamboo Shoot Mountains\Nare the only ones you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:04:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Bamboo Shoot Mountains are the best,\Nbut... Ah! Pokee can be good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Pokee," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the standard when it comes to snacks.\NThey're just so crunchy and delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know of them! I've heard that in Japan,\Nfriends will engage in a Pokee game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A Pokee game...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what sort of game it is, UMR?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Uh, I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I would like to do it with you,\Nthis so-called Pokee game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,U-uh, no, no way! That's not a game that we would play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?! I wish to do it with you, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about the Pokee game, is, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You have to do it with someone\Nwho's really SPECIAL to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think of you as a MOST special friend, UMR!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think the same of you, but there's NO WAY\Nwe're playing the Pokee game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Sorry for raising my voice like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just, I don't think that's the kind of game\Nthat friends play with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right. It's my fault for getting carried away\Nat having a friend over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's nice having this big room and all,\Nbut I bet it's lonely having her snack feasts all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm the one who's sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... you're a great friend, TSF!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I'm SUPER embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Let's watch some anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let's play the Pokee game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They play the Pokee game even in anime.\NI wonder what sort of game it is, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here goes. We each take one end, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we're getting closer and closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, so, that's why... we can't do it, right?\NThe Pokee game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A-agreed! My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi there, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry to put you out, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She really did come for bread day, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I made enough for the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I've made curry and naan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The deuce, you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice and chewy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Hikari, Kanau knows you've been coming here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I thought, she doesn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanau!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Taihei?! C-can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about before. It took longer\Nthan expected to wrap things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wrap up...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: Kanau mistakenly confuses the meaning of "to get someone home,"\Nfor the homophone "to return something."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: Kanau mistakenly confuses the meaning of "to get someone home,"\Nfor the homophone "to return something."\NDid I lend you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaruuun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, is it possible you've been coming here without\Nsaying anything? That would make your sister worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Big Brother, why don't you call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! Th-there's no need!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it IS more dangerous at night,\Nand she's probably made dinner already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:08:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister works overtime on Tuesdays.\NI've just been eating on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Well, we don't mind at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be working late tonight,\Nbut I've made dinner and put it in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I've gotta eat alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, fine, if there's no other option...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up or it'll get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you don't need me to walk you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm meeting someone, so I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, Big Brother? Is it all right if I come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come whenever you like, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't make a habit of coming every week, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing, Hikari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari! You went out tonight, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar! I know you've been going out\Non Tuesdays when I work overtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I only went to get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to be out this late, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought for sure you'd object when Hikari said\Nshe wanted to come over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,N-nah, I don't really mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it, TSF?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,UMR, didn't this used to be a beauty shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're right! TSF, had you been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No. But it had an old-timey feel, and I liked it, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's indeed a shame when a shop you like goes away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You do like retro-style buildings,\Ndon't you? I do too, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you sure know a lot about old-school\Ndepartment stores and candy shops,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you lived in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I do! Such things are nostalgic, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nostalgic"? You've got\Nthe same kind of stuff in Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no. But I'd been to Japan once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was six, I made quite the fuss\Nuntil I was brought here for some sightseeing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Making such a fuss that they brought her\Nfrom Germany here to Japan is pretty impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:11:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I came, I saw an old arcade\Nwith a beautiful lake and a giant swan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful memory, one that I've kept to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do you want to head out there today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right. I don't remember where it is,\Nand I doubt it exists anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's probably that mecca for retro gamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm somewhat afraid, UMR.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If the scenery has changed from how I remember it...\NI think it would be a bit of a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, TSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying the same is what makes the mecca a mecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely unchanged!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sagamiko Park hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The buildings are the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the signs are the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same store employee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's the all-important pinball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, even that is the same as back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up. The Swan Boat is gonna leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,TSF, there's a rare game over here\Nthat I've never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like most of the people\Non those boats are couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylph, why don't you want to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because after today, we'll go back to Germany!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I... I won't be able to see Big Brother anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't said a word since I mentioned couples...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,TSF? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,UMR, let's ride one of those boats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT'S where this conversation led to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup! Whoa! This thing is shaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've been on a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my all-knowing hero, UMR. You'll be fine indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hardly all-knowing. I only knew about\Nthe Sagamiko arcade because it's famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,UMR!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean, "Thank you for BRINGING me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's perfectly fitting, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this again. I'll come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tests start tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling confident, Umaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There sure is a lot we have to know this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it, Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to fail tomorrow's tests...\NI might not even make it to the next grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you mean, you won't make it to the next grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but this is the day before exams!\NWhy are you only now...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The timing just didn't feel right.\NI hope I pass along with the rest of you, but maybe I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what is at stake here, then this where I come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall hold a study group, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-this is one amazing library...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a wealth of books here,\Nand the silence most certainly lends itself to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Umaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even been in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thrilled at the idea of having\Na study session with you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I don't think this is the right time to feel "thrilled."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, what would you say are your weakest subjects?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A-all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's just see how things go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a pretty decent grasp of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be enough to get you\Nabout an 80. Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, I think you have performance anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That time before when we studied together,\Nyou did just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But later, when we took the test,\Nit looked like you didn't do so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone gets so serious when we're taking tests...\Nit's like a totally different classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if I'm the only one\Nwho gets left behind by the flow of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Reckon things could go wrong at the drop of a hat,\Nand I'd just wanna up and go back to Akita!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that must mean some seriously bad grades!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,S-so then, so long as you're not nervous,\Nyou should be able to get a passing grade, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but... what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I personally think of people as vegetables\Nor something and purge them from my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She always does that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you may be able to relax\Nif you think about something you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-th-that might make me worry even MORE!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she imagine something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, this is sort of vexing. The test is tomorrow,\Nbut we haven't found a way to solve things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You all have your own studying to do,\Nbut you're taking the time to help ME...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm just dragging you all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-in any case, right now\Nwe need less tears and more ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, that's right! We're sure to find\Na sound solution if we put our heads together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ebina. Wipe those tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,E-everyone, why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start memorizing, Ebina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphin, that's not the subject for tomorrow's test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, learn THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez... Sylphin, you're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My first day at a new school...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm kinda nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're from the Midwest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the Northwest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Those girls over there've already made friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I want some friends too.\NReckon I gotta talk to someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll try talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That Motoba girl kinda lost it\Nat the entrance ceremony, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that right. They say\Nshe kicked some guy, a grownup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. She left...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll try inviting her out for lunch sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a pleasure to meet you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Sylphinford Tachibana, and I shall become\Nthe greatest "player" in this classroom, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shbafeeeen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-she's... like... outta some magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll be able to talk to her, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, it's nice to meet you. Ebina is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ebina S. Maineim"? That's a rather unusual name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, no, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Ebina."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:19:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet! You're quite courageous to be the first one\Nto come talk to me. That is the spirit, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I challenge you, Ebimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Ebina"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, a challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, at whatever you would say you are best at.\NCome at me with anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe challenges like this are normal in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As for what I'm "best at"... I'm no good at studying,\Nthough I'm not bad at cooking and household chores...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I can't do those now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can eat a lot of akitakomachi rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't have any akitakomoachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,'Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaruuuun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Reckon she's like a princess and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:20:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Umaru Doma, yes? I heard you took\Nthe top spot in the entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I don't know if I was at the top or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You will now challenge me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So her name's "Umaru Doma."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, be quick! It's a challenge!\NA challenge, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if maybe one day me\Nand these girls can be friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay? It looked like you were spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because Sylphin keeps acting all weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So now I am the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Really, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all study together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, start your tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now and forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, I'll race you to that utility pole over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-why would I want to do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because seeing who comes first\Nwould be a challenge indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,H-how about we all go eat some crepes or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being so welcoming with my sister Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.08,0:23:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We have yet to spend\Nany proper time together yet, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,M-maybe we can go have tea or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, s-sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Awkward...
